    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered since day one, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019ve absolutely loved every mile in this beauty, and honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let her go. She\u2019s in truly stunning shape\u2014the kind of car you park at the end of the lot just to keep her pristine. You might find a tiny character mark if you look with a magnifying glass, but she shines like she just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve kept up with every bit of maintenance because I believe cars like this deserve the best. Come by, let's chat cars, and get you behind the wheel of your dream ride!",
